Coming for a drink in the board room? Thanks.

7
00:01:16,887 --> 00:01:20,163
趁足球俱乐部还在 好好享受吧
Ah, well, better enjoy it while the club's still here.

8
00:01:21,367 --> 00:01:24,325
我们一向能撑过去的     这次不一样
